import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset


val claimText = sc.parallelize(
    IOUtils.toString(
        new URL("file:///C:/Users/224597/Downloads/SQL/CLAIMS_DRAG_ISSUE_2.csv"),
        Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

case class Claims(DRAG_DATE: String, DRAG_INDICATOR: String, CLAIM_ID: String)

val claims = claimText.map(s => s.split(",")).filter(s => s(0) != "\"DRAG_DATE\"").map(
    s => Claims(s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(1).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(2).replaceAll("\"", "")
        )
).toDF()
claims.registerTempTable("claim")
